	</table>
</div><br />
<br />
<b>Thank you for this reasonable and well thought out post. I will ask the team about it. If I have any news to pass along, I will post it here.</b><br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
