</div> <br />
<br />
<b>Howdy,<br />
 <br />
I did mention that rangers do need some poking and prodding, perhaps some upgrades in some key areas, that does not mean that anything will be taken away.  However, if rangers were to receive all of the things they want, we would have to remove other abilities.  We cannot allow one class to have everything they want, simply because they want it.  We then end up with one class.  Where is the fun in that? <br />
 <br />
You do have the right to voice your complaints but that does not mean we can or should make every change you complain for.  We have a responsibility to the 15 other classes as well.  As much as you hate any of your abilities being given away, so do they.  We want the game to be fun, and believe it or not, most folks (even rangers) are having fun.  <br />
 <br />
So, would an increase to melee dpw make the game more fun for you?  Perhaps some discs or AAs related to dps output?  Some of what I see suggests that it would help.  Let's hear some more on that point please.</b><br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
