				<div style="font-style:italic">Howdy,<br />
I did mention that rangers do need some poking and prodding, perhaps some upgrades in some key areas, that does not mean that anything will be taken away. However, if rangers were to receive all of the things they want, we would have to remove other abilities. We cannot allow one class to have everything they want, simply because they want it. We then end up with one class. Where is the fun in that?</div>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div> <br />
The only answer can be: no fun whatsoever. While I agree with you that you cannot give away the earth to one group of people, you can make reasonable adjustments to bring a class back into focus. I believe that is what is at the base of our requests other than "Give Rangers Ice Comet, Backstab, Harm Touch, and Complete Heal OMG!!!". <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" class="inlineimg" /> <br />
 <br />
