				<div>Originally Posted by <strong>Brenlo</strong></div>
				<div style="font-style:italic">So, would an increase to melee dpw make the game more fun for you? Perhaps some discs or AAs related to dps output? Some of what I see suggests that it would help. Let's hear some more on that point please.</div>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div>I've updated my original post above with some more detailed suggestions. Please take the time to review them. <br />
 <br />
Thanks for the replies, keep them coming!<br />
 <br />
~Aluyen</div>
