<i>Brenlo, <br />
Look, DPS is DPS, whether from a bow or melee weapons. You know that, and we know that. Why SOE feels ranged combat is worse for Rangers than it is for all the casters that fight from well away from the mobs is beyond me. Personally I don't care. And that is with the understanding that my current capabilities with bows will not diminish, as you pointed out.<br />
