		<div>Well, the biggest things I really want are these:<br />
  <br />
  1. Increase Melee DPS (a non-AA melee discipline perhaps?)<br />
  <br />
  2. New harmony for levels up to 70<br />
  <br />
 3. Running speed increase (it's almost as if you need a bard to pull now, from my experience in Wall of Slaughter. I did get lucky with snare pulling, but I know not all spots in the zone, let alone all zones, will be that easy to pull with snare.)<br />
  <br />
 4. Increase L50+ nuke damage slightly, and lower the cast time. Keep the recast time the same 30 seconds. This way, the time it takes to cast the spell doesn't take away from archery or melee DPS, which in most cases it currently does.<br />
  <br />
 5. I think the Strength of Tunare line should be more powerful (so people will actually bother with it, rather than it being a waste of a spell) and should stack with brells, and spiritual vigor lines, thus providing another reason Rangers will be wanted in groups. With the increasing buff slots from alternate advancement, this should be welcomed.</div>
